msgid "TXT_DLG_SCRIPT03_D3032_THEND"
msgstr "Then die in shame and dishonour."

msgid "TXT_DLG_SCRIPT06_D0_AHASU"
msgstr ""
"Ah, a surfacer in need of a favour. Down here you do a favour to get a "
"favour and I need the town entrance that is our path to food opened. The "
"Order has it sealed and guarded."

msgid "TXT_DLG_SCRIPT06_D1516_DOMYF"
msgstr "Do my favour first, or you'll get squat from me."

msgid "TXT_DLG_SCRIPT10_D33352_WELLW"
msgstr ""
"Well, what is it now? Don't you ever take a break? I'm glad that you're "
"still breathing. I'd hate for my favourite student to come back looking out "
"from the inside of a body bag."

msgid "TXT_RYES0_SCRIPT18_D1516_THETE"
msgstr "The templar's favourite weapon."

msgid "TXT_RPLY0_SCRIPT23_D1516_LEATH"
